<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.4.11">
<l>cītanīrpuṭai cūḻceḻuṅkaḻa ṉiyuṭaittiruk kōṭṭiyūr</l>
<l>ātiyāṉaṭi yāraiyumaṭi maiyiṉṟittiri vāraiyum</l>
<l>kōtilpaṭṭarpi rāṉkuḷirputu vaimaṉviṭṭu cittaṉcol</l>
<l>ētamiṉṟiyu raippavarkaḷi ruṭīkēcaṉuk kāḷarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who flawlessly pronounce the words of</l>
<l>Viṭṭucittaṉ, King of cool Putuvai, Lord of faultless scholars</l>
<l rend="indent">about those who are devotees of the Primal Lord</l>
<l rend="indent">and those who wander without serving [the Lord]</l>
<l rend="indent">in Tirukkōṭṭiyūr with fertile fields</l>
<l rend="indent">surrounded on [all] sides by cool waters</l>
<l>are servants of Hṛṣīkeśa.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
